INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2426,'2426','2016-12-13T08:28:23Z',1077,9,'HGustavs','Closed','Keeping track of marking preview','Currently when one clicks the preview to viewedit the results of a sutdent and click a document we are automatically moved bakc to the list of all students when we go back from the pdf document. One would prefer a solution that uses histories or local storage to remember that we were displaying the results of a specific student.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2427,'2427','2016-12-13T08:30:41Z',1077,9,'HGustavs','Closed','Marking list row number','It would be nice to have an over-sized number for each visible row in the marking view as the left column. 1 for the first visible student  and 2 for the second etc. Not the number in the dataset  but the sequence number of currently visible students.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2428,'2428','2016-12-13T08:33:43Z',1077,9,'HGustavs','Closed','Marking view column click behavior','When clicking on a purple heading in the marking view we change the sorting function to be the logical one for that column e.g. most recent unmarked for most column or last name for student. When clicking on the orange hading in the marking view we change the direction of the sort  if it currently is ascending we change to descending ...');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2429,'2429','2016-12-13T08:43:15Z',1077,9,'HGustavs','Closed','Marking preview is ugly','Several things are ugly here. Styling of preview list box with interior shadows and rounded corners. It does not look like anything else. Standardize the look to look like something else we already have. The P button gives us a popup preview  the link gives us a full screen pdf document. I would like to reverse this  to place the full screen pdf in the P burtton the preview in the link. A you-tube-like full screen icon instead of a horribly styled button containing a P. The support-person-headset-feedback-icon in the icon folder instead of the feedback text button. The headings in the preview file table do not clearly indicate that they are headings e.g. no borders or colors etc. [https:cloud.githubusercontent.comassets697880121133181ea06d6c2-c117-11e6-8041-e4384b7c2039.png]');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2430,'2430','2016-12-13T10:02:41Z',1077,11,'HGustavs','Closed','Magic hedings in resulted is not properly formated','We do not have the upper heading only the subheding The heding text is not vertically aligned in the magic headings');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2431,'2431','2016-12-13T20:56:14Z',1077,21,'a97marbr','Closed','When hovering over an empty cell highlightcolumn is too short','As title suggests. Hovering over an empty cell in the resulted will generate a too short highlight border.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2432,'2432','2016-12-13T20:59:47Z',1077,21,'a97marbr','Closed','Re-clicking on header will not resort','If we click once on a header it will resort on that header. Clicking again will do nothing. Clicking yet again will resort properly. This pattern will repeat it self ... every second click on the same column will trigger a resort.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2433,'2433','2016-12-13T21:03:00Z',1077,22,'a97marbr','Closed','If we have magic headings showing and we click on them for resort they disappear','If we have magic headings showing and we click on them for resort they disappear. On scrolling they will reappear properly formatted.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2434,'2434','2016-12-14T12:37:04Z',1078,13,'a97marbr','Closed','I want a generic accordion widget','We really could use a generic accordion widget similar to this: https:jqueryui.comaccordion We already have some code written for this. There is one in generic file dugga and another one in file list. It should be generic and work with the color and sizes used in LenaSYS');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2435,'2435','2016-12-20T19:46:27Z',1084,20,'HGustavs','Closed','Filter view in result editor is cleared to no filtering if the login times out while viewing result editor','A better way to do this is to not update the filter property if not logged in  currently it seems that it is cleared if user does not have permission.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2436,'2436','2016-12-21T07:54:04Z',1085,8,'a97marbr','Closed','Using a direct link to a page that requires login is shown to guest','There does not seem to be a proper credentials check for showdoc. Using a direct link to a page that requires login is served by showdoc to guest');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2437,'2437','2017-01-09T10:49:39Z',1104,11,'HGustavs','Open','Read only mode for backup site use','We have a backup machine for lena that is mirrored for assignments and so on  but as we do not synchronize in the oposite direction we need a read only mode on that machine  which alllows the user to view code examples  assignments etc but not submit data or edit examples etc which only should be possible on the real machine');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2438,'2438','2017-01-09T10:51:48Z',1104,11,'HGustavs','Closed','css formatting breaks when reviewing submission','In the marking view  when we review the submission  upon return from that modal dialog the high-lighting breaks on the main result table.  due to approx 50px table padding on result table.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2439,'2439','2017-01-09T10:54:28Z',1104,11,'HGustavs','Closed','Resort after changing mark does not update contents','The contents of the in-memory-sorted result table is not updated fully. Sort the table on last submit Mark one student assignment Assignment is shown as marked in table Sort again Now we expect no change... but... we get the table without the marked result until we refresh the page.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2440,'2440','2017-01-09T10:56:23Z',1104,11,'HGustavs','Closed','If blank filter list we need some output','We need a filter list is blank output if filter list is blank  currently nothing happens.... which may confuse the user to thing that the code is broken.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2441,'2441','2017-01-09T10:58:56Z',1104,11,'HGustavs','Closed','Students groups in various views','Assignning groups to students in access list and supporting per-group markinghandinassignments If student A and B collaborate in a group we would want this to be represented somehow. Unclear as to exact details.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2442,'2442','2017-01-09T22:31:55Z',1104,23,'a97marbr','Open','Choose https over http for student submissions if LenaSYS is run over HTTPS','If the LenaSYS system is accessed over HTTPS we will get issues with HTTP urls in the system. Submitting none https urls will not be viewable in some of the views  e.g.  results view and dugga preview . We need to address this in some way. For example by suggesting when uploading a link that HTTPS is preferred  required? ');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2443,'2443','2017-01-10T12:56:55Z',1105,13,'HGustavs','Closed','Magic headings can some times be above popover modal dialog','It is somewhat intermittent. Unclear if this is due to clicking outside of the popover  or one touches scroll wheel on a mouce scrolls on touchpad or for some other reason. [https:cloud.githubusercontent.comassets6978801218069387b993ba4-d73c-11e6-8351-d55cb8602cf2.png]');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2444,'2444','2017-01-10T12:57:39Z',1105,13,'HGustavs','Closed','Search filtering in marking result view','What title says.');
INSERT INTO issue VALUES(2445,'2445','2017-01-10T12:59:37Z',1105,13,'HGustavs','Closed','Marking view sorting functionality in all tables','There are tables all over in the interface. I think that the interface could benefit from using the sorting functionality from the marking view. For example  the file lists  being able to filter  or to sort on dateuser name etc would be a great feature for courses with hundreds of files.');
